snippet.textDisplay: Coming from someone who's dealt with Endometriosis since I was like 14, there is no "test" to see if you have it. You can't get an ultrasound or anything to see if anything's in there. Surgery is the only way right now to figure that out. That being said, an excision surgery is not horrible to go through and doesn't have a ton of down time. All that being said, I sure hope its NOT endometriosis because it is a giant PITA to deal with and go through.
